OL,3,CStarmer fails to comment on calls for
OL,4,CKing to meet Epstein victims
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fdeclined to comment on whether the
OL,8,FKing should meet with victims of
OL,9,Fpaedophile financier Jeffrey Epstein
OL,10,Fduring a state visit next month.
OL,12,FKing Charles has faced calls from the
OL,13,Ffamily of Epstein victim Virginia
OL,14,FGiuffre to meet with survivors during
OL,15,Fhis April visit to the US.
OL,17,FStarmer said the visit will focus on
OL,18,Fthe 250th anniversary of American
OL,19,Findependence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
