PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer fails to comment on calls for
OL,4,CKing to meet Epstein victims
OL,6,F"In relation to the King, I think it's
OL,7,Fimportant to appreciate this is part
OL,8,Fof the 250 celebrations," the prime
OL,9,Fminister said.
OL,11,F"It's a long-planned visit, and the US
OL,12,Fand UK are close allies, have been for
OL,13,Fa very, very long time."
OL,15,FThere are no plans for the King and
OL,16,FQueen to meet any survivors and
OL,17,Fvictims of Epstein.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@XO]
