OL,3,CStarmer fails to comment on calls for
OL,4,CKing to meet Epstein victims
OL,6,FITV News understands that the ongoing
OL,7,Fpolice investigation into the King's
OL,8,Fbrother, Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor,
OL,9,Fwill prevent any such meeting from
OL,10,Ftaking place.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FBuckingham Palace confirmed on Tuesday
OL,18,Fthat the King and Queen will visit
OL,19,FWashington, despite calls for the trip
OL,20,Fto be postponed due to the on-going
OL,21,Fconflict in the Middle East.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
