OL,3,CStarmer fails to comment on calls for
OL,4,CKing to meet Epstein victims
OL,6,FRo Khanna, a Democrat US congressman,
OL,7,Fhas also called on the King to meet
OL,8,Fsurvivors during the state visit.
OL,9,FKhanna helped to convince the US
OL,10,FJustice Department to release the
OL,11,Fmillions of Epstein files and make
OL,12,Fthem available to the public.
OL,14,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,15,Fweekly podcast about the royal family,
OL,16,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,17,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
